---
title: Indonesian-Style Fried Rice with Sesame Fried Eggs
description: This rice is absolutely choccas with veggies and all the delicious notes of the Indonesian classic nasi goreng. Topped off with a fried egg for ultimate yolk ooziness, easy weeknight suppers have never looked so good.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5b63dd6330006c0355529f76-6aa6ae8c.jpg
